HEADWORD: Cephalometer
<hw>Ceph`a*lom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Cephalo-</ets> + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
